posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 33', 'OR Text', '33', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 968 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Step into The Sinclair: The stuff that life is made of.', 'Our newly built vintage chic community in Port Orchard presents 1, 2 & 3 bedroom homes.', 'Each private apartment provides well-organized space and storage options along with immaculate, stylish appliances and designer fixtures and lighting.', 'Relax outside on your private deck or patio with community, pool and wooded views.', 'Upgrade features available including plank flooring and advanced connectivity.', 'Experience our club house, outdoor grills, playgrounds, fitness center and convenient car detailing area.', 'Don’t wait, Contact The Sinclair today!', 'Features:', 'Extra Storage, Patio/Balcony, Garbage Disposal, Dishwasher, Efficient Appliances, Full Size Washer/Dryer in Home, Internet/Cable Ready', 'Community Amenities:', 'Car Detailing Area, Recycling, Pet Friendly, On-Site Maintenance, BBQ/Picnic Area, Valet Trash Service, Seasonal Heated Pool, Off Street Parking, Secured Garages, Walking Trails, 24/7 Fitness Center, High Speed Internet, Covered Carports, Playground, Resident Lounge, Amazon Lockers, Business Center, On-Site Management, EV Charging Stations', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats & Dogs allowed.', '2 pets per household.', 'One-time $600 non-refundable pet fee & additional $200 for 2nd pet.', 'Pet rent is $25 a month and $45 monthly for two', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5x rent to gross income ratio (household)', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', 'rEvPQyg3']
